::KitKat::

She looked at him with a surpized look.  She wondered why he would do 
that. No bot ever did that before.  She smiled. "Thanks. But if 
Megatron finds out. I'll get zapped again. He may even have me 
scrapped." She looked him and thought she saw something. She couldn't 
put her finger on it.  Did he really like her, she thought. "I know 
that I can accomplish the mission if given enough time to work out a 
good plan. I know that if I could hand over the ship to megatron, 
he'd be pleased. But, ah heck, I don't know. Terrorsaur would have to 
in on it too. He'd be a key player in all this. He's the only one 
that could fly. But...he hates the idea." she looked at her drink 
again. "Unless the whole team worked together, it would never work 
out. That's my biggest problem right there." She took a sip of her 
drink and looked again at the glass.
